 symbols).\n- `fn_8001EBF0` improves from 98.77% to 99.23% fuzzy match by folding `ALIGN_32` into a single-assignment site.\n\n## Functions matched\n\nNo new 100% matches in this PR — this is a readability/naming follow-up to #2504 with one minor fuzzy-match improvement (`fn_8001EBF0`: 98.77% → 99.23%).\n\n## Files\n\n- `src/melee/lb/lbmthp.c`\n- `src/melee/lb/lbmthp.h`\n- `src/melee/lb/lbmthp.static.h`\n\n## Verification\n\n- `python configure.py && ninja` → green (`build/GALE01/main.dol: OK`)\n- All other modules including `lbmthp.h` still build cleanly (mn, gm consumers verified)\n- Match status of every previously-matched function in `lbmthp.c` preserved","created_at":"2026-05-16T20:17:55Z","updated_at":"2026-05-16T20:27:14Z","closed_at":"2026-05-16T20:21:58Z","merged_at":"2026-05-16T20:21:58Z","merge_commit_sha":"9e3d894779d7b345dffec307d9833436a99b170a","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2506/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2506/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2506/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/7d4f8c7b52f7ff5868f75a6e0037c062846fabad","head":{"label":"itsgrimetime:pr/lb-mthp-naming","ref":"pr/lb-mthp-naming","sha":"7d4f8c7b52f7ff5868f75a6e0037c062846fabad","user":{"login":"itsgrimetime","id":990274,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk5MDI3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/990274?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime","html_url":"https://github.com/itsgrimetime","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/u